  "detailed_description": "※Sex is not included. Please note.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575450/extras/168d27a72154f8a3abc4af028202c686.avif?t=1750393547\" width=616 height=400 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575450/extras/4d211df8d6f03fbed903e57f6bac2f8d.avif?t=1750393547\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br>\"It's strange. According to the schedule, we should have already arrived at our destination...\"<br>\"God, watch over us.\"<br><br>As you wake up and wake up, you can see the Dark Siren wandering around inside the empty ship looking for you.<br>What the hell happened here?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575450/extras/e1389b087047dbd97e15864ed726bd31.avif?t=1750393547\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br>Find the notes left by the sailors throughout the ship, uncover the truth about what happened here, and escape.<br>You must stay alert and look around carefully to avoid being charmed by the Dark Siren.<br>If you are caught and enchanted by the Dark Siren 3 times, the game will be over.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575450/extras/c76f263e0328343fc916320a66758603.avif?t=1750393547\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br>▷ Charming characters<br>▷ Suspenseful play<br>▷ Simple operation<br>▷ Game Mode: Normal Mode, Hard Mode, Invisible Mode<br>▷ Various skins that can be unlocked while playing<br>▷ 7 achievements<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575450/extras/b4b4d9c8e5883ca9a526b529f945d751.avif?t=1750393547\" width=616 height=400 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "※Sex is not included. Please note.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575450/extras/168d27a72154f8a3abc4af028202c686.avif?t=1750393547\" width=616 height=400 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575450/extras/4d211df8d6f03fbed903e57f6bac2f8d.avif?t=1750393547\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br>\"It's strange. According to the schedule, we should have already arrived at our destination...\"<br>\"God, watch over us.\"<br><br>As you wake up and wake up, you can see the Dark Siren wandering around inside the empty ship looking for you.<br>What the hell happened here?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575450/extras/e1389b087047dbd97e15864ed726bd31.avif?t=1750393547\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br>Find the notes left by the sailors throughout the ship, uncover the truth about what happened here, and escape.<br>You must stay alert and look around carefully to avoid being charmed by the Dark Siren.<br>If you are caught and enchanted by the Dark Siren 3 times, the game will be over.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575450/extras/c76f263e0328343fc916320a66758603.avif?t=1750393547\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br>▷ Charming characters<br>▷ Suspenseful play<br>▷ Simple operation<br>▷ Game Mode: Normal Mode, Hard Mode, Invisible Mode<br>▷ Various skins that can be unlocked while playing<br>▷ 7 achievements<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575450/extras/b4b4d9c8e5883ca9a526b529f945d751.avif?t=1750393547\" width=616 height=400 /></span>",
